node.text:
Do you know how the Cigar band was born? 💨 
In the 18th century, Catherine the Great, Empress of Russia, was a great lover of cigars. However, one part of cigar smoking she didn’t enjoy was the stains left behind on her fingers after enjoying a good smoke. To protect her royal fingers, it is believed that she asked for her cigars to be wrapped in small pieces of silk. And so, the tale goes, the cigar band was born.
Share you thoughts below 👇🏻

#cigaraficionado
